
隐私政策

最后更新日期：2024年4月25日

感谢您使用招财应用（以下简称"本应用"）。本隐私政策旨在向您说明我们如何收集、使用、存储和保护您的信息。请您仔细阅读以下内容，以便了解我们的隐私保护实践。

1. 我们收集的信息

本应用仅收集以下信息：

- 使用数据：应用内的游戏数据，如您累积的金币数量。
- 设备动作数据：我们使用设备的运动传感器来检测摇晃动作，以实现应用的核心功能。
- 阅读数据：应用会从我们的服务器获取每日运势阅读内容。

2. 信息的使用

我们收集的信息仅用于以下目的：

- 提供、维护和改进本应用的功能
- 记录您在应用中的游戏进度（金币数量）
- 提供每日运势阅读服务

3. 信息的存储

- 本地存储：您的金币数量仅存储在您的设备本地，使用iOS的UserDefaults系统。
- 数据保留：您的数据将保留在您的设备上，直到您卸载应用或清除应用数据。

4. 信息的共享

我们不会与任何第三方共享您的个人信息。本应用：

- 不收集个人身份信息
- 不包含第三方分析工具
- 不使用广告服务
- 不跟踪用户行为用于营销目的

5. 数据安全

我们采取合理的技术措施来保护您的信息：

- 所有数据仅存储在您的设备本地
- 应用与服务器之间的通信使用安全的HTTPS协议

6. 您的权利

您对自己的数据拥有完全控制权：

- 您可以随时通过应用内的"销账"功能清除您的金币数据
- 您可以通过卸载应用来删除所有本地存储的数据

7. 儿童隐私

本应用不针对13岁以下的儿童。我们不会故意收集儿童的个人信息。

8. 隐私政策的变更

我们可能会不时更新本隐私政策。更新后的政策将在应用内公布，并标注更新日期。

9. 联系我们

如果您对本隐私政策有任何疑问或建议，请通过以下方式联系我们：

moneytreeapp2025@gmail.com


Privacy Policy

Last Updated: April 25, 2024

Thank you for using the Money Tree app ("the App"). This Privacy Policy is designed to inform you about how we collect, use, store, and protect your information. Please read the following carefully to understand our privacy practices.

1. Information We Collect

The App only collects the following information:

- Usage Data: In-app game data, such as the number of coins you have accumulated.
- Device Motion Data: We use your device's motion sensors to detect shaking motions to enable the core functionality of the App.
- Reading Data: The App fetches daily fortune reading content from our server.

2. Use of Information

We use the collected information solely for the following purposes:

- To provide, maintain, and improve the App's functionality
- To record your game progress (coin count) within the App
- To provide daily fortune reading services

3. Storage of Information

- Local Storage: Your coin count is stored only locally on your device using iOS's UserDefaults system.
- Data Retention: Your data is retained on your device until you uninstall the App or clear the App data.

4. Sharing of Information

We do not share your personal information with any third parties. The App:

- Does not collect personally identifiable information
- Does not include third-party analytics tools
- Does not use advertising services
- Does not track user behavior for marketing purposes

5. Data Security

We take reasonable technical measures to protect your information:

- All data is stored locally on your device only
- Communication between the App and our server uses secure HTTPS protocol

6. Your Rights

You have complete control over your data:

- You can clear your coin data at any time using the "销账" (Clear Account) feature in the App
- You can delete all locally stored data by uninstalling the App

7. Children's Privacy

The App is not directed at children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated policy will be posted in the App with the updated date.

9. Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

moneytreeapp2025@gmail.com
